Use 'pxx
ssh' instead of psmstart. 'ssh -x' is still default.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4639 | eicker | 2007-03-09 15:52:03 +0100 (Fri, 09 Mar 2007) | 3 lines

Update copyright.
Fix some svn properties.

